きっと
surely

338
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:06,040
困難じゃないはず
it shouldn't be too hard.

339
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:09,240
信じてみよう
Let's believe in it.

340
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:10,840
私は
I am sure

341
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:14,040
こんなんじゃないはず!
I'm not meant to be like this!

342
00:28:24,540 --> 00:28:26,540
3, 2, 1, GO!

343
00:28:37,040 --> 00:28:41,040
こんなんじゃない!
I'm not meant to be like this!

344
