[Song: Great Days]

345
00:29:03,540 --> 00:29:09,040
Shining justice 芽生えて
Shining justice, now budding inside,

346
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:14,840
Brand new bed town 交差する息吹
Brand new bed town, intersecting breaths.

347
00:29:15,040 --> 00:29:17,840
岬から潮風
A salty breeze blows from the cape,

348
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:20,540
トンネル抜け鉄塔へ
heading through the tunnel toward the steel tower.

349
00:29:20,540 --> 00:29:25,840
引かれ合い小道に迷い込む
Attracted to each other, getting lost on a path.

350
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:28,040
ココロに
Into my heart,

351
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:33,240
溶け込む影
a shadow melts away,

352
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:37,240
照らす黄金の "Spirits"
illuminating the golden "Spirits."

353
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:43,040
それは守り抜く光
That is the light we'll protect to the end.

354
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:48,040
Let the voice of love take you higher

355
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:54,040
集まるチカラで時さえ越えて
With our gathered strength, we will even transcend time.

